data.description: Surrender yourself to the charms of this cul-de-sac traditional-style townhouse on a placid street near public transportation/recreation/schools. Notables include a finished walk-out basement, a formal dining room, and large rooms. Space galore. Light and airy floorplan, ambiance, ideally spacious living and family rooms. Ceiling fans. Work-at-home office. Laminate, ceramic tile flooring. Earth-tone decor, master suite. Attractive large bedrooms, ceramic tile baths with separate shower, soaking tub, and a food storage area. Eat-in kitchen. All-kitchen appliance package, gleaming stainless-steel appliances, gas range. Upper and lower patios. Community lake fishing, park, and picnic areas. Walking paths, here are great looks, plus lots of great living! Prompt possession.
